generation_strategy_gap:
Strategy: GAP IDENTIFICATION
Instruction: Identify approaches NOT yet tested in this specific flow based on the context. Propose novel methodologies that logically stem from the data. Frame as: "Given the absence of [gap in current approaches], we propose [novel approach]." Generate hypotheses that represent new concepts, ensuring they are fundamentally different from the following existing hypotheses:
{existing}

generation_strategy_cross_domain:
Strategy: CROSS-DOMAIN TRANSFER
Instruction: Leverage methodologies from adjacent industries (e.g., polymers, composites, chemical processing). Adapt these external technologies to this metallurgical challenge. Frame as: "Adapting [technology] from [adjacent field], we propose [adaptation] for [target]." Create highly unique approaches that do not overlap with the following existing hypotheses:
{existing}

hypothesis_output_format:
Return a JSON array of objects strictly matching this schema:
[
  {
    "statement": "Формулировка гипотезы (1-3 предложения)",
    "mechanism": "Механизм воздействия с количественными данными (3-5 предложений)",
    "citations": ["ссылка на источник 1", "ссылка на источник 2"],
    "reasoning_trace": "Пошаговое логическое обоснование валидности гипотезы"
  }
]
